### BUG-01: CRA + Vite Conflict (App Won't Build)
**Problem:** `main.jsx` imports `import App from './App.jsx'` and uses `ReactDOM.createRoot` (Vite), but `package.json` has `react-scripts` (CRA) as the build tool. `index.js` also exists alongside `main.jsx`.  
**Impact:** `npm run build` will fail or produce incorrect output in production.

**Fix — Choose Vite (recommended):**
